###
### ========= OTP Endpoints =========
###

### 2. Generate an OTP for a user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/otp/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "sricharan@example.com"
}

###
### 3. Verify an OTP (SUCCESS CASE)
# Check your VS Code terminal for the generated OTP and paste it here
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "sricharan@example.com",
  "otp": "PASTE_THE_6_DIGIT_OTP_HERE"
}

###
### 4. Verify an OTP (FAILURE CASE - WRONG OTP)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "sricharan@example.com",
  "otp": "999999"
}